questions.quote: Joey, Ross is gonna be here any second, would you mind watching Ben for me while I use the ladies' room?
Well, there was that one time that Monica and Rachel got together.

Oh, hey, my pleasure. So what are your intentions with my Phoebe?
Guys, I'd listen to her. The vein is bigger than I've ever seen it.
Yeah, well, I'll take a little crying any day over Howard-the-"I-win"-guy. "I win! I win!" I went out with the guy for two monthsI didn't get to win once.
